column2: SELECT P.ObjID FROM PhotoPrimary AS P JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#, #, #) AS GN ON P.objID = GN.objID JOIN Neighbors AS N ON P.ObjID = N.ObjID JOIN PhotoPrimary AS L ON L.ObjID = N.NeighborObjID WHERE  P.ObjID < L. ObjID and abs((P.u-P.g)-(L.u-L.g))<# and abs((P.g-P.r)-(L.g-L.r))<# and abs((P.r-P.i)-(L.r-L.i))<# and abs((P.i-P.z)-(L.i-L.z))<#
